sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant DynamicToolSelection
    participant ToolRegistry
    participant DynamicModelSelection
    participant ModelRegistry

    Agent->>DynamicToolSelection: Request Tool (Task Requirements)
    DynamicToolSelection->>ToolRegistry: Discover Tools (Capabilities, Permissions)
    ToolRegistry-->>DynamicToolSelection: Available Tools
    DynamicToolSelection->>DynamicToolSelection: Evaluate Tools (Reliability, Latency)
    DynamicToolSelection-->>Agent: Selected Tool
    Agent->>Agent: Execute Task with Selected Tool

    Agent->>DynamicModelSelection: Request LLM (Task Requirements)
    DynamicModelSelection->>ModelRegistry: Discover Models (Capabilities, Cost, Latency)
    ModelRegistry-->>DynamicModelSelection: Available Models
    DynamicModelSelection->>DynamicModelSelection: Evaluate Models (Performance, Security)
    DynamicModelSelection-->>Agent: Selected LLM
    Agent->>Agent: Execute Task with Selected LLM
